<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<p>
This Privacy Policy describes how <strong>Store Sort Saga</strong> (“we”, “our”, or “us”) handles information
when you use our mobile game application.
</p>

<p>
Store Sort Saga is a <strong>puzzle game designed for children and families</strong>. Protecting the privacy of
children is extremely important to us.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

<p>
<strong>We do not collect any personal information.</strong>
</p>

<p>
The game does NOT collect:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Names</li>
    <li>Email addresses</li>
    <li>Phone numbers</li>
    <li>Location data</li>
    <li>Photos or videos</li>
    <li>Voice recordings</li>
    <li>Device identifiers</li>
</ul>

<p>
All gameplay data (such as levels completed) is stored locally on the device only and is never shared.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>2. Children’s Privacy (COPPA Compliance)</h2>

<p>
Store Sort Saga is suitable for children under the age of 13 and complies with the
<strong>Children’s Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA)</strong>.
</p>

<p>
We do not knowingly collect, request, or store any personal data from children.
Parents can safely allow their children to play without providing any personal information.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>3. Ads</h2>

<p>
This app <strong>does not display any advertisements</strong>.
</p>

<p>
There are no third-party ad networks integrated into Store Sort Saga.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>4. Analytics & Tracking</h2>

<p>
We do <strong>not use analytics tools</strong>, tracking technologies, or behavioral profiling.
</p>

<p>
No user behavior is monitored, tracked, or analyzed.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>5. In-App Purchases</h2>

<p>
Store Sort Saga does not include in-app purchases.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>6. Internet & External Links</h2>

<p>
The game does not require an internet connection to play.
</p>

<p>
There are no external links or social media integrations inside the app.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>7. Data Security</h2>

<p>
Since no personal data is collected, stored, or transmitted, there is no risk of data leakage or misuse.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>

<p>
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.
Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>9. Contact Us</h2>

<p>
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:
</p>

<p>
<strong>Email:</strong> your-email@example.com
</p>

<hr>

<p>
<em>Last updated: December 2025</em>
</p>

